deck: In a world where "People" live in horrid, squalid slums and "Citizens" enjoy comforts in splendid "City." The only way up and out is to fight. But, what is really there at the end of the battle? Grey Death is determined to find out and to survive!
description: This is the story of Grey Death, an outsider and a fighter destined to figure out what happens when you become a citizen. It is a world where the "haves" are regulated to clockwork precision by the central computer Toy, and the "have-nots" are sentenced to the worst dregs of squalid slums. The only way for a slum dweller to get out of poverty is to fight. The question is, is the prize at the end of the battle worth getting there?
name: Grey
